com.google.android.exoplayer2.extractor.mp3

Interface Mp3Extractor.Seeker

  • All Superinterfaces:
    SeekMap
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ConstantBitrateSeeker, VbriSeeker, XingSeeker
    Enclosing class:
    Mp3Extractor

    static interface Mp3Extractor.Seeker
extends SeekMap
    SeekMap that also allows mapping from position (byte offset) back to time, which can be used to work out the new sample basis timestamp after seeking and resynchronization.
